    <item>
      <title>CrowdStrike 和全球 IT 中断的解释</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/crowdstrike-microsoft-it-outage-what-caused-it-what-comes-next</link>
      <description><![CDATA[7 月 19 日星期五，CrowdStrike Holdings Inc. 发生大规模 IT 故障，导致航班停飞、市场混乱、全球企业陷入混乱。CrowdStrike 股价一度下跌 15%。此次中断的影响预计将持续数天，而微软 Azure 云服务的一个看似无关的问题加剧了此次中断的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/crowdstrike-microsoft-it-outage-what-caused-it-what-comes-next</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 16:40:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰警告黑海船只 GPS 导航出现故障</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/ukraine-warns-ships-that-satnav-is-being-scrambled-in-black-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰海港管理局警告船东不要依赖关键的导航工具，因为黑海的卫星通信系统日益受到干扰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/ukraine-warns-ships-that-satnav-is-being-scrambled-in-black-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 16:31:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CrowdStrike 崩溃迫使全球各地的计算机手动重启</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/crowdstrike-gaffe-forces-manual-reboot-of-computers-around-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[造成此次网络故障的网络安全公司 CrowdStrike Holdings Inc. 在周五的一份声明中表示，周五发生的全球 IT 故障导致所有受其影响的 Windows 计算机都需要手动重启。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/crowdstrike-gaffe-forces-manual-reboot-of-computers-around-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 15:19:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>私人信贷、银行竞相资助独家网络收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/private-credit-banks-compete-to-fund-exclusive-networks-buyout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，私人信贷基金和银行正在商谈提供高达 10 亿欧元（11 亿美元）的资金，用于资助对法国网络安全专家 Exclusive Networks SA 的潜在收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/private-credit-banks-compete-to-fund-exclusive-networks-buyout</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 14:17:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联邦快递、UPS 警告称全​​球技术故障将导致快递延迟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/ups-warns-of-delivery-delays-from-global-technology-outage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦快递公司和联合包裹服务公司警告称，由于大规模 IT 故障正在颠覆市场、使全球各地的公司陷入瘫痪，快递公司正努力应对这种故障带来的影响，包裹递送可能出现延误。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/ups-warns-of-delivery-delays-from-global-technology-outage</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 13:07:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球 IT 崩溃使网络公司 CrowdStrike 成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-it-collapse-puts-cyber-firm-crowdstrike-in-spotlight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[导致航班停飞、市场混乱、全球企业陷入瘫痪的大规模 IT 故障的背后是一家网络安全公司：CrowdStrike Holdings Inc.]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-it-collapse-puts-cyber-firm-crowdstrike-in-spotlight</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 12:18:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大规模技术故障导致全球医院陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-it-outage-is-hitting-doctor-appointments-across-the-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受全球数字中断影响，从航空旅行到紧急服务等重要资源陷入混乱，世界各地的卫生系统取消了相关程序，转而使用手写记录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-it-outage-is-hitting-doctor-appointments-across-the-uk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 10:21:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>航空公司开始设法摆脱严重航班中断的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-aviation-grinds-to-halt-as-united-delta-stop-operations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在全球大规模软件崩溃之后，航空公司开始缓慢恢复部分运营，但数千个航班的延误或取消可能会持续数天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-aviation-grinds-to-halt-as-united-delta-stop-operations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 08:22:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球 IT 崩溃导致 911 呼叫中断、飞机停飞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/microsoft-cloud-service-issues-disrupt-air-travel-operations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[网络安全公司 CrowdStrike Holdings Inc. 的一次失败的软件更新导致全球无数的 Microsoft Windows 计算机系统崩溃，这将成为全球有史以来最严重的 IT 故障。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/microsoft-cloud-service-issues-disrupt-air-travel-operations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 03:31:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
